All Classes

Class
Description
Animal
The abstract class Animal represents an animal with properties such as mammal, carnivorous, and mood.
AnimalMoods
The AnimalMoods enum represents the possible moods of an animal.
Cat
The class Cat represents a domestic cat.
Dog
The class Dog represents a domestic dog.
Frog
The class Frog represents a frog that is an animal living both on land and in water.
getWater
The interface getWater represents an animal that lives in water.
Land
The Land interface represents an animal that lives on land.
TestAnimal
The TestAnimal class is used to test the behavior and functionality of the animal classes.
